title: 188: How Much for a Round Trip
itunes:title: How Much for a Round Trip
description: Mike tells the amazing story of a mostly forgotten explorer, whose epic journey helped pave the path to Mars. Then, he’s joined by everyone’s favorite astronomer, Dr. Michelle Thaller, to better understand what the hell is happening on the Red Planet, and why it’s so frickin' expensive to get there.
itunes:author: The Way I Heard It with Mike Rowe
